        <h1 class="label">Biography</h1>
        <div class="govspeak">
<p>Ian Ferguson is a non-executive board member of the Department for Education. He joined in January 2016.</p>

<p>Heâ€™s also a member of the <a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/groups/efa-advisory-group">Education Funding Agency Advisory Group</a>.</p>

<p>In 1981 he founded Metaswitch Networks , a company that develops telecommunications software.</p>

<p>Ian received a CBE for services to education and training in 2005.</p>
</div>
